{"tid":1731500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得好嬲 好無力 冇方向 有啲頹嘅你入嚟望下！！！","createTime":"2019-11-17T17:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T18:09:28.000Z","uid":307651,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a47c8cad870d11eb1988cf1d703a4d7587f8dbe1","tid":1731500,"uid":307651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"p牌仔第一次開post有咩錯漏有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一，麻煩大家記返起我哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不割蓆，不分化</strong></span></span>嘅原則，唔好再話留守喺埋大嘅人點點點，一早話咗要散點點點，有咩唔啱有咩不滿等全世界都安全先再檢討啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個時候我地更加要齊心啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，依家唔理三七廿一，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有嘢就做咗先啦</span></strong></span>！無論依家落街食宵夜散步遊下車河又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，留係屋企睇map做哨做文宣又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，甚至係瞓覺準備聽朝晨曦活動都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，千祈唔好猶豫，即管繼續做，唔好覺得咁樣救唔到仲喺埋大嘅手足！要記得我哋係點走過依五個月，咩都好，唔試過又點知結果啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，見到有啲人話集中救埋大手足，聽日啲活動取消，但計我話，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">why not both</span></strong></span>！依家一大堆人盡力營救手足唔小心救到天光又唔小心多人到塞住條路大家都冇心㗎嘛係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前嗰幾個月嘅抗爭日程咪又係水蛇春咁長，我哋都參加得哂啦，依家區區兩個活動算得啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果仲喺poly嘅手足睇到依個post嘅話，我想同你哋講返聲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">我愛你地啊</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地今日打得好型，見到水炮車都唔撚驚真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打咗咁耐辛苦哂你哋，我哋入緊嚟啦你哋要頂多陣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後嘅最後，大家記住依一世都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔可以原諒班人渣黑警</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌哂佢哋老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">祝大家武運隆昌<br />\n願榮光歸香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c0d575f967f6df1f8ac284a020b28db53f302ad1","tid":1731500,"uid":307651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"p牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbea41d4eef1c8482b79812dc791478234833e5","tid":1731500,"uid":307651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:41:16.000Z","msg":"入嚟吸收下正能量再捱過今晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9a844eea72558c55b2ce0090cb6f5e4076c68e","tid":1731500,"uid":269301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517565baa2001d336da77d2b2286df5226634ca6","tid":1731500,"uid":307651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"開完post又要繼續行街街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edde48d65ff19aef2c34152055be46c23a3ad149","tid":1731500,"uid":322524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:42:22.000Z","msg":"做怨婦唔係呢個moment , 動搖軍心以前打仗會點㗎"},{"pid":"4be9f1dd709f504b93eba1b069c066dffdb0d2db","tid":1731500,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,